# ─── Rust ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Catches the workspace `target/` at the repo root AND any excluded
# crate's own `target/` next to its Cargo.toml. Note: `oracle` is
# intentionally excluded from the workspace per Cargo.toml, so it
# produces `oracle/target/` which the previous anchored `/target`
# pattern did NOT cover.
target/
**/*.rs.bk

# Coverage profiles (cargo-llvm-cov, tarpaulin, grcov)
*.profraw
*.profdata
tarpaulin-report.html
lcov.info
cobertura.xml

# ─── Oracle / SQLite runtime state ───────────────────────────────────
# Oracle persists fleet state, audit log, and step progress to SQLite
# (see oracle/README.md → Persistence). Devs running the daemon
# locally will produce DB files; never commit them.
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

# ─── Environment / secrets ───────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# ─── Future Tauri pantheon (Node.js side) ────────────────────────────
node_modules/

# ─── Logs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log

# ─── Patch / merge debris ────────────────────────────────────────────
*.orig
*.rej

# ─── IDEs and editors ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
.fleet/
.zed/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ─── OS metadata ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
